{"tid":737733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有女狀元指對時事感興趣　形容劉霞可往德國是重獲自由","createTime":"2018-07-11T04:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T10:33:33.000Z","uid":24824,"like":49,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1a2263149bbdba91468a5f2ef2a920350486fbb5","tid":737733,"uid":24824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"中學文憑試今日放榜，9位學生考獲7科或以上5**，分別是6男3女。<br />\n<br />\n來自拔萃女書院的狀元林悅兒說，自己在數學科必修部份的考試，無法計算出部份答案，所以對最終考獲佳績感到驚喜。她又表示對醫學有熱誠，而且喜歡與病人溝通，計劃於本地大學升讀醫科。她認為本港醫院醫生短缺，輪候專科需時甚長，有可能令病人病情惡化，建議政府改善醫療系統。<br />\n<br />\n另一位女拔狀元梁芷喬說，自己對時事感興趣，將於牛津大學就讀哲學、政治和經濟學。她對諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波遺孀劉霞，獲准前往德國感高興，形容她重獲自由，又指中國人權問題有待改善。<br />\n<br />\n她表示未知將來會否投身政界，要待學成返港後再作決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406346-20180711.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406346-20180711.htm&d=voP7tq0CdGeXI%2FGEQLZGcwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=868840ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406346-20180711.htm&h=fd7abf29\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406346-20180711.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5f355f85642650bce013f841c55a436203d97eac","tid":737733,"uid":98167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb475d961a22f606b82e8ae9d972cb2acd0103b","tid":737733,"uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:53:01.000Z","msg":"呢條女冇運行"},{"pid":"a5afdad4e2ca99917576a4533c699caaace5cf9f","tid":737733,"uid":24824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f355f85642650bce013f841c55a436203d97eac","tid":737733,"uid":98167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img s